1
00:00:35,900 --> 00:00:38,300
=Angels and Guards=

2
00:00:38,333 --> 00:00:41,133
=Episode 22=

3
00:00:42,200 --> 00:00:45,133
As the saying goes,
it takes two to start a fight.

4
00:00:45,433 --> 00:00:47,033
Even if the female Jinyiwei
were at fault,

5
00:00:47,066 --> 00:00:48,066
Li Qingshan

6
00:00:48,066 --> 00:00:49,300
is no saint either.

7
00:00:49,533 --> 00:00:50,966
And now you want

8
00:00:51,500 --> 00:00:53,833
my carefully trained female Jinyiwei
killed?

9
00:00:54,166 --> 00:00:55,866
I will be the first to disagree.

10
00:00:57,200 --> 00:00:58,266
Commander Zhang.

11
00:00:58,433 --> 00:00:59,766
Killing government soldiers

12
00:01:00,033 --> 00:01:02,033
is a grave crime against the throne.

13
00:01:02,700 --> 00:01:04,133
Don't give me that.

14
00:01:04,400 --> 00:01:05,833
Are my Northern Bureau officers mad?

15
00:01:06,433 --> 00:01:07,300
Would they just

16
00:01:07,766 --> 00:01:09,666
fight government troops for no reason?

17
00:01:10,166 --> 00:01:12,900
The truth has not even been made clear.

18
00:01:12,900 --> 00:01:15,500
You can't take Li Qingshan's word alone

19
00:01:15,533 --> 00:01:16,700
and kill my people.

20
00:01:18,500 --> 00:01:19,700
Besides,

21
00:01:20,066 --> 00:01:21,333
maybe those

22
00:01:21,900 --> 00:01:23,733
thugs from the Governor's Office

23
00:01:23,900 --> 00:01:24,933
took a liking to our female Jinyiwei

24
00:01:25,233 --> 00:01:26,500
and tried to take advantage of them.

25
00:01:26,600 --> 00:01:27,466
Think about it.

26
00:01:27,733 --> 00:01:28,733
Could they have

27
00:01:29,266 --> 00:01:30,200
framed them?

28
00:01:30,500 --> 00:01:32,666
Now you are being unreasonable.

29
00:01:35,266 --> 00:01:37,033
Now you want to reason?

30
00:01:37,900 --> 00:01:38,766
Let me tell you.

31
00:01:39,400 --> 00:01:40,500
Not with me.

32
00:01:41,600 --> 00:01:42,300
Mr. Zhang.

33
00:01:42,733 --> 00:01:43,966
Don't cause a scene here.

34
00:01:44,266 --> 00:01:45,533
This is a place of state affairs.

35
00:01:48,600 --> 00:01:49,533
Oh?

36
00:01:50,066 --> 00:01:51,633
Oh, really?

37
00:01:52,333 --> 00:01:53,566
So that is how you want to play it?

38
00:01:53,900 --> 00:01:54,833
Fine.

39
00:01:56,233 --> 00:01:57,433
You all heard that?

40
00:01:57,733 --> 00:01:58,800
You all heard him?

41
00:01:59,066 --> 00:01:59,833
Good!

42
00:02:00,500 --> 00:02:02,100
Today, I will not just raise hell.

43
00:02:02,366 --> 00:02:03,866
I will pee right here if I have to.

44
00:02:04,233 --> 00:02:05,566
Let me show you how wild I can be.

45
00:02:05,766 --> 00:02:06,833
I would like to see

46
00:02:07,266 --> 00:02:08,833
what the Grand Secretary

47
00:02:08,866 --> 00:02:10,466
can do to the Commander
of the Northern Bureau

48
00:02:10,733 --> 00:02:12,300
and His Majesty's own
Left Army Commander.

49
00:02:13,666 --> 00:02:14,100
Your Majesty.

50
00:02:14,766 --> 00:02:16,933
The three female Jinyiwei
of the Northern Bureau

51
00:02:17,500 --> 00:02:18,900
came into conflict

52
00:02:18,900 --> 00:02:20,566
with guards at the Yunnan border
relay station.

53
00:02:21,700 --> 00:02:23,266
It happened because Li Qingshan,
Governor of Yunnan,

54
00:02:23,366 --> 00:02:24,533
had received Cabinet orders

55
00:02:24,533 --> 00:02:25,633
to eliminate Fa Yuanrong.

56
00:02:26,066 --> 00:02:27,600
Eager to claim credit,

57
00:02:27,900 --> 00:02:29,600
Li didn't inform Baihu Shen.

58
00:02:30,066 --> 00:02:31,766
Baihu Shen and the others thought
the officers were impostors

59
00:02:32,033 --> 00:02:33,200
sent to assassinate Fa Yuanrong.

60
00:02:33,700 --> 00:02:34,766
That's what led to the clash.

61
00:02:35,033 --> 00:02:36,466
I ask Your Majesty to investigate.

62
00:02:38,100 --> 00:02:38,933
Is that so?

63
00:02:39,600 --> 00:02:41,300
(His Majesty reeks of wine.)

64
00:02:41,600 --> 00:02:42,166
(Perfect.)

65
00:02:43,433 --> 00:02:44,200
Your Majesty.

66
00:02:44,766 --> 00:02:46,600
You drank again last night,
didn't you?

67
00:02:48,666 --> 00:02:50,233
Only a few cups.

68
00:02:51,766 --> 00:02:52,300
Your Majesty,

69
00:02:53,000 --> 00:02:53,500
this is

70
00:02:53,833 --> 00:02:56,433
a sobering pill made by Xu Duoyu
of the Northern Bureau.

71
00:02:58,500 --> 00:03:00,600
Take it before drinking,
and you can hold a thousand cups.

72
00:03:00,866 --> 00:03:02,866
Take it after, and it clears the head.

73
00:03:03,600 --> 00:03:04,666
It works that well?

74
00:03:13,733 --> 00:03:15,066
Send word to Duoyu.

75
00:03:15,400 --> 00:03:16,800
Have him send the formula

76
00:03:17,233 --> 00:03:18,166
to the Imperial Pharmacy.

77
00:03:18,833 --> 00:03:19,400
Yes, Your Majesty.

78
00:03:20,433 --> 00:03:20,800
Then,

79
00:03:21,166 --> 00:03:23,700
about the three female Jinyiwei
and the soldiers...

80
00:03:28,833 --> 00:03:30,433
Spare me all the excuses.

81
00:03:30,433 --> 00:03:33,000
If you don't give me an answer today,

82
00:03:33,166 --> 00:03:35,266
I'm moving in right here.

83
00:03:35,533 --> 00:03:37,466
I will have someone bring my luggage

84
00:03:37,600 --> 00:03:38,666
and my quilts,

85
00:03:38,766 --> 00:03:39,266
and I

86
00:03:39,733 --> 00:03:41,100
will settle in.

87
00:03:42,066 --> 00:03:42,933
My lord, please.

88
00:03:43,933 --> 00:03:44,600
Shameless.

89
00:03:44,933 --> 00:03:45,800
Zhang Weimin.

90
00:03:47,033 --> 00:03:48,366
You are disturbing the Cabinet.

91
00:03:49,233 --> 00:03:51,633
Don't you fear
His Majesty's punishment?

92
00:03:51,933 --> 00:03:55,033
Now you remember His Majesty?

93
00:03:55,166 --> 00:03:56,766
Fine. You want to report me?

94
00:03:56,866 --> 00:03:58,200
Go ahead.

95
00:03:58,366 --> 00:03:59,800
You think I don't know?

96
00:04:00,866 --> 00:04:01,966
Forming cliques,

97
00:04:02,233 --> 00:04:03,300
plotting behind closed doors,

98
00:04:03,533 --> 00:04:04,800
all of it was under your direction.

99
00:04:05,533 --> 00:04:06,033
You...

100
00:04:06,400 --> 00:04:07,566
You are slandering me!

101
00:04:08,100 --> 00:04:09,200
What proof do you have?

102
00:04:10,066 --> 00:04:10,833
Imperial edict!

103
00:04:16,366 --> 00:04:16,933
(Imperial Edict)
Imperial command.

104
00:04:17,400 --> 00:04:18,100
Upon investigation,

105
00:04:18,500 --> 00:04:19,600
the case involving
the three female Jinyiwei

106
00:04:19,600 --> 00:04:21,200
and the soldiers under

107
00:04:21,233 --> 00:04:22,233
the Governor of Yunnan

108
00:04:22,333 --> 00:04:23,366
contains many doubts.

109
00:04:23,666 --> 00:04:24,900
The three female Jinyiwei
injured government soldiers,

110
00:04:25,233 --> 00:04:26,466
a serious crime in itself.

111
00:04:26,866 --> 00:04:28,766
(Imperial Edict)
But soldiers under the Governor's Office

112
00:04:28,766 --> 00:04:30,000
acted without authority

113
00:04:30,066 --> 00:04:33,400
and attempted to murder Prince Yuanrong
of Liao, also a grave crime.

114
00:04:33,600 --> 00:04:34,466
Left Commander

115
00:04:34,500 --> 00:04:36,733
and Northern Bureau
Commander Zhang Weimin

116
00:04:36,866 --> 00:04:38,566
shall discuss
the three women's offenses

117
00:04:38,566 --> 00:04:39,633
with the Cabinet.

118
00:04:39,666 --> 00:04:41,833
No execution shall be ordered rashly.
By imperial order.

119
00:04:42,266 --> 00:04:44,933
Long live His Majesty.

120
00:04:54,600 --> 00:04:55,366
Come here.

121
00:04:55,400 --> 00:04:56,666
Governor...

122
00:04:56,700 --> 00:04:57,866
I knew it.

123
00:04:58,066 --> 00:04:59,300
Once you stepped in,

124
00:04:59,333 --> 00:05:00,933
I knew it would be fine.

125
00:05:00,933 --> 00:05:02,933
Good wine is on me today.

126
00:05:03,933 --> 00:05:05,133
Today, thanks to Xu Duoyu's

127
00:05:05,166 --> 00:05:06,600
homemade sobering pill,

128
00:05:06,600 --> 00:05:08,200
His Majesty was quite pleased.

129
00:05:08,666 --> 00:05:09,100
Don't worry.

130
00:05:09,366 --> 00:05:10,533
I will reward him when we return.

131
00:05:13,433 --> 00:05:14,133
Zhang.

132
00:05:15,100 --> 00:05:15,766
Young Duke.

133
00:05:16,733 --> 00:05:17,566
Since

134
00:05:18,100 --> 00:05:19,133
His Majesty has ordered

135
00:05:19,433 --> 00:05:20,500
that mercy be shown,

136
00:05:21,000 --> 00:05:21,933
the Cabinet has decided

137
00:05:22,433 --> 00:05:24,100
to let the three female Jinyiwei

138
00:05:25,166 --> 00:05:26,333
redeem themselves through service.

139
00:05:26,733 --> 00:05:27,800
If they succeed,

140
00:05:27,933 --> 00:05:29,100
their crime will be pardoned.

141
00:05:29,933 --> 00:05:31,366
If they fail...

142
00:05:33,000 --> 00:05:34,100
Then their crimes

143
00:05:34,500 --> 00:05:35,933
will be counted together.

144
00:05:36,166 --> 00:05:37,533
Shen Bingfan and the other two

145
00:05:37,700 --> 00:05:38,566
must capture

146
00:05:38,766 --> 00:05:40,700
the phantom thief Feng Fuliu
within three days.

147
00:05:41,500 --> 00:05:42,533
If they succeed,

148
00:05:42,700 --> 00:05:43,800
they will be spared.

149
00:05:44,433 --> 00:05:45,433
If they fail,

150
00:05:45,766 --> 00:05:46,633
they will be executed at once.

151
00:05:47,366 --> 00:05:48,266
Three...

152
00:05:50,533 --> 00:05:52,466
That is the Cabinet's final decision.

153
00:05:55,333 --> 00:05:56,400
Three days, then.

154
00:06:09,566 --> 00:06:10,100
Beiming.

155
00:06:16,066 --> 00:06:16,666
You are back.

156
00:06:18,433 --> 00:06:19,600
You went to plead with the Emperor?

157
00:06:20,366 --> 00:06:20,900
Yes.

158
00:06:21,600 --> 00:06:23,133
It was dangerous,

159
00:06:23,400 --> 00:06:24,766
but luckily, His Majesty

160
00:06:25,366 --> 00:06:27,033
may not like attending court,

161
00:06:27,400 --> 00:06:28,100
but

162
00:06:28,766 --> 00:06:30,466
he hates being played for a fool.

163
00:06:30,700 --> 00:06:32,466
Li Qingshan, the Governor of Yunnan,

164
00:06:33,033 --> 00:06:33,800
teamed up with the Cabinet,

165
00:06:34,166 --> 00:06:36,000
along with Duan Li
and Princess Pingyang,

166
00:06:36,533 --> 00:06:38,300
to push for your deaths.

167
00:06:38,933 --> 00:06:40,266
That only made His Majesty suspect

168
00:06:40,533 --> 00:06:41,566
they were forming a faction.

169
00:06:41,766 --> 00:06:43,266
So when I pleaded for you,

170
00:06:43,533 --> 00:06:44,900
he did me this favor.

171
00:06:45,700 --> 00:06:47,700
But the price is catching Feng Fuliu.

172
00:06:51,100 --> 00:06:52,333
Yes. I will help you catch him.

173
00:06:52,600 --> 00:06:53,766
Isn't that what you always wanted?

174
00:06:56,766 --> 00:07:00,500
♪This longing I cannot say♪

175
00:07:01,833 --> 00:07:02,433
Beiming.

176
00:07:03,766 --> 00:07:04,533
If we catch Feng Fuliu,

177
00:07:05,666 --> 00:07:07,066
will it really not hurt you?

178
00:07:07,333 --> 00:07:08,000
Why?

179
00:07:09,666 --> 00:07:11,400
You think I can't beat him?

180
00:07:11,733 --> 00:07:12,433
No.

181
00:07:13,200 --> 00:07:13,966
I'm just afraid...

182
00:07:14,166 --> 00:07:15,033
Don't be.

183
00:07:16,166 --> 00:07:17,066
There is nothing to fear.

184
00:07:18,866 --> 00:07:19,633
As for you,

185
00:07:21,066 --> 00:07:22,266
you will be fine.

186
00:07:23,700 --> 00:07:24,466
And as for me,

187
00:07:25,000 --> 00:07:26,033
you never need to worry.

188
00:07:30,400 --> 00:07:34,800
♪Afraid love will fade like smoke♪

189
00:07:36,633 --> 00:07:43,566
♪Afraid memories will fade like dreams♪

190
00:07:43,600 --> 00:07:46,966
♪This longing I cannot say♪

191
00:07:46,966 --> 00:07:53,866
♪Tucked away inside my heart♪

192
00:07:54,966 --> 00:08:00,700
♪Afraid love will fade like smoke♪

193
00:08:01,200 --> 00:08:08,066
♪Afraid memories will fade like dreams♪

194
00:08:08,100 --> 00:08:11,633
♪This longing I cannot say♪

195
00:08:11,633 --> 00:08:18,533
♪I wish you could hear♪

196
00:08:19,400 --> 00:08:24,100
♪Afraid love will fade like smoke♪

197
00:08:25,700 --> 00:08:32,600
♪Afraid memories will fade like dreams♪

198
00:08:32,800 --> 00:08:36,333
♪This longing I cannot say♪

199
00:08:36,333 --> 00:08:41,233
♪Tucked away inside my heart♪

200
00:08:48,400 --> 00:08:49,000
Young Master Chang.

201
00:08:50,866 --> 00:08:51,466
This time,

202
00:08:51,933 --> 00:08:54,266
thank you for entering the palace
and saving us.

203
00:08:55,400 --> 00:08:56,666
No need to thank me, Hua.

204
00:08:57,500 --> 00:08:58,733
But how are we supposed

205
00:08:59,833 --> 00:09:01,700
to catch Feng Fuliu in three days?

206
00:09:06,033 --> 00:09:06,700
One step

207
00:09:07,366 --> 00:09:08,133
at a time.

208
00:09:10,866 --> 00:09:12,300
We were reckless this time.

209
00:09:13,100 --> 00:09:14,500
Strictly speaking,

210
00:09:15,366 --> 00:09:16,566
we don't have much ground
to stand on.

211
00:09:17,600 --> 00:09:19,000
So pull yourselves together.

212
00:09:19,600 --> 00:09:20,600
Make up for your mistake

213
00:09:21,066 --> 00:09:21,966
by earning merit.

214
00:09:24,900 --> 00:09:26,166
Young Master Chang,

215
00:09:26,700 --> 00:09:27,633
you really are calm

216
00:09:28,366 --> 00:09:29,533
as a mountain.

217
00:09:32,433 --> 00:09:33,366
What choice do I have?

218
00:09:34,700 --> 00:09:36,566
If I'm falling apart inside,

219
00:09:37,533 --> 00:09:38,433
I might as well pretend to be calm.

220
00:09:39,500 --> 00:09:40,566
At least I will look good doing it.

221
00:09:43,100 --> 00:09:45,300
But what happens after three days?

222
00:09:49,600 --> 00:09:50,466
After three days?

223
00:09:53,500 --> 00:09:55,333
I let you catch Feng Fuliu.

224
00:09:56,033 --> 00:09:56,633
Young Master Chang.

225
00:09:57,166 --> 00:09:59,166
Playing with fire is no joke.

226
00:09:59,866 --> 00:10:00,633
Don't worry.

227
00:10:02,366 --> 00:10:03,933
I would never gamble

228
00:10:04,533 --> 00:10:05,600
with my life

229
00:10:06,833 --> 00:10:07,600
or the three of yours.

230
00:10:14,033 --> 00:10:15,133
(Emerald Pavilion)

231
00:10:15,166 --> 00:10:15,666
(Emerald Pavilion)
Hua.

232
00:10:16,100 --> 00:10:18,000
I heard the Yudai River
has a lovely view.

233
00:10:18,566 --> 00:10:19,600
No, no.

234
00:10:19,733 --> 00:10:20,566
My animal sign is "cat".

235
00:10:20,666 --> 00:10:21,366
I hate water.

236
00:10:23,266 --> 00:10:24,133
I heard

237
00:10:24,700 --> 00:10:27,033
there is a purple bamboo grove
outside Xizhi Gate.

238
00:10:27,900 --> 00:10:29,833
We could go there instead.

239
00:10:30,933 --> 00:10:32,133
Can't we go to both?

240
00:10:32,733 --> 00:10:34,000
Please.

241
00:10:34,333 --> 00:10:37,200
One is east, one is west.
There's no time.

242
00:10:41,400 --> 00:10:42,933
What are you doing?

243
00:10:44,700 --> 00:10:46,300
Deciding where to have fun.

244
00:10:47,533 --> 00:10:47,966
Have fun?

245
00:10:48,066 --> 00:10:48,933
Ladies,

246
00:10:49,433 --> 00:10:50,833
you have only three days

247
00:10:50,866 --> 00:10:51,533
to catch Feng Fuliu.

248
00:10:52,033 --> 00:10:53,133
And you still want to play?

249
00:10:54,100 --> 00:10:55,766
We are not catching Feng Fuliu.

250
00:10:56,166 --> 00:10:59,400
So we want to use our last three days

251
00:10:59,733 --> 00:11:01,633
to enjoy ourselves.

252
00:11:04,000 --> 00:11:05,533
Poor old me.

253
00:11:05,533 --> 00:11:07,533
I nearly killed myself saving you.

254
00:11:07,700 --> 00:11:10,200
And look at you now.

255
00:11:11,000 --> 00:11:12,500
Eating, playing, and waiting to die.

256
00:11:14,766 --> 00:11:15,766
Who are you trying to fool?

257
00:11:16,566 --> 00:11:18,000
You don't want to live, do you?

258
00:11:18,666 --> 00:11:19,900
Let me tell you.

259
00:11:20,700 --> 00:11:22,866
Once you join the Jinyiwei,

260
00:11:23,333 --> 00:11:25,333
your lives are no longer your own.

261
00:11:26,533 --> 00:11:28,366
Then punish us as you see fit, my lord.

262
00:11:30,533 --> 00:11:31,366
Childish.

263
00:11:33,066 --> 00:11:33,833
Stubborn.

264
00:11:35,200 --> 00:11:35,566
Foolish.

265
00:11:36,233 --> 00:11:36,933
So foolish.

266
00:11:38,533 --> 00:11:40,766
Have you forgotten your mission?

267
00:11:41,233 --> 00:11:43,000
Have you forgotten how hard

268
00:11:43,100 --> 00:11:44,133
you fought

269
00:11:44,433 --> 00:11:45,866
to get into my Northern Bureau?

270
00:11:48,733 --> 00:11:51,133
You risked your lives for promotion.

271
00:11:52,100 --> 00:11:53,533
For what?

272
00:11:54,233 --> 00:11:55,733
You suffer one little grievance,

273
00:11:56,433 --> 00:11:57,833
and now you sulk at me?

274
00:11:59,533 --> 00:12:00,633
What is the point?

275
00:12:02,100 --> 00:12:02,633
But

276
00:12:03,433 --> 00:12:04,800
we can't catch Feng Fuliu.

277
00:12:07,700 --> 00:12:09,033
Then at least

278
00:12:09,233 --> 00:12:10,433
pretend.

279
00:12:10,500 --> 00:12:12,833
Pretend you are trying to catch him.

280
00:12:13,933 --> 00:12:16,933
I'm not asking you to worship me
for saving you.

281
00:12:17,100 --> 00:12:17,633
But first,

282
00:12:18,866 --> 00:12:20,533
you did kill government soldiers.

283
00:12:20,600 --> 00:12:21,966
That part is true, isn't it?

284
00:12:26,866 --> 00:12:28,066
At least earn

285
00:12:28,333 --> 00:12:29,233
some merit

286
00:12:29,700 --> 00:12:31,066
to offset your fault.

287
00:12:32,933 --> 00:12:34,433
My lord! My lord!

288
00:12:34,600 --> 00:12:36,466
Are you all right? What is wrong?

289
00:12:38,066 --> 00:12:39,933
Then send us back
to the Imperial Prison.

290
00:12:39,933 --> 00:12:40,700
My lord!

291
00:12:42,266 --> 00:12:42,500
Go!

292
00:12:43,266 --> 00:12:44,033
Make them leave!

293
00:12:44,266 --> 00:12:44,866
Leave!

294
00:12:44,900 --> 00:12:46,500
I don't want to see them.

295
00:12:47,433 --> 00:12:48,433
Just go!

296
00:12:48,933 --> 00:12:50,700
My lord, are you all right?

297
00:12:53,833 --> 00:12:54,600
My lord!

298
00:13:12,733 --> 00:13:13,466
Mr. Lu.

299
00:13:16,400 --> 00:13:17,166
What brings you here?

300
00:13:18,766 --> 00:13:20,000
I came to return this.

301
00:13:24,533 --> 00:13:25,266
You must be mistaken.

302
00:13:25,600 --> 00:13:26,466
Is that mine?

303
00:13:29,233 --> 00:13:29,766
Oh.

304
00:13:30,533 --> 00:13:32,133
Then perhaps I remembered wrong.

305
00:13:33,233 --> 00:13:34,266
But this pouch says

306
00:13:34,533 --> 00:13:35,633
that Jinyiwei on assignment

307
00:13:36,166 --> 00:13:37,533
may act at their own discretion
in the field.

308
00:13:38,366 --> 00:13:40,600
It also says Jinyiwei can't
take on two missions at once.

309
00:13:41,433 --> 00:13:43,433
Only after the first mission
is complete

310
00:13:43,733 --> 00:13:44,966
may they receive the next one.

311
00:13:46,433 --> 00:13:48,033
So what exactly

312
00:13:48,700 --> 00:13:49,966
was the senior who gave me this
trying to say?

313
00:13:51,166 --> 00:13:53,833
Maybe he was afraid
you would lose your judgment

314
00:13:54,233 --> 00:13:55,433
or be led astray.

315
00:13:57,900 --> 00:13:58,666
Mr. Lu.

316
00:13:59,500 --> 00:14:00,500
Whatever misunderstandings

317
00:14:00,833 --> 00:14:01,600
you may have about me

318
00:14:02,266 --> 00:14:03,033
or the female Jinyiwei,

319
00:14:04,000 --> 00:14:05,033
in my heart,

320
00:14:05,866 --> 00:14:08,566
you will always be the finest Jinyiwei
in the Northern Bureau.

321
00:14:20,166 --> 00:14:22,400
(Northern Bureau)

322
00:14:24,500 --> 00:14:24,866
Who is there?

323
00:14:24,866 --> 00:14:25,433
Who is there?

324
00:14:27,066 --> 00:14:28,166
I will see what it is.

325
00:14:33,033 --> 00:14:33,533
A challenge letter?

326
00:14:34,200 --> 00:14:35,433
(The Phantom Thief Feng Fuliu)
The phantom thief Feng Fuliu

327
00:14:35,933 --> 00:14:37,600
greets Mr. Zhang of the Jinyiwei.

328
00:14:37,933 --> 00:14:39,300
Tomorrow, on the night
of the full moon,

329
00:14:39,433 --> 00:14:40,666
I shall come to you

330
00:14:41,066 --> 00:14:42,733
and borrow the imperial Twin Dragon
Jade.

331
00:14:44,233 --> 00:14:45,266
Summon Lu Guokai at once.

332
00:14:48,866 --> 00:14:50,966
Feng Fuliu has challenged
the Northern Bureau!

333
00:14:51,900 --> 00:14:53,933
Feng Fuliu has challenged
the Northern Bureau!

334
00:14:55,066 --> 00:14:57,300
Feng Fuliu has challenged
the Northern Bureau!

335
00:14:57,600 --> 00:14:58,100
Hua.

336
00:14:59,066 --> 00:14:59,733
Hua.

337
00:15:00,233 --> 00:15:01,133
Bad news, Hua!

338
00:15:02,533 --> 00:15:03,100
Hua.

339
00:15:03,766 --> 00:15:04,166
Hua.

340
00:15:05,033 --> 00:15:06,066
Coming.

341
00:15:06,666 --> 00:15:07,866
It's the middle of the night.

342
00:15:07,866 --> 00:15:08,933
Why are you shouting?

343
00:15:11,866 --> 00:15:12,533
What are you looking at?

344
00:15:13,533 --> 00:15:14,933
Keep staring, and I will gouge
your eyes out.

345
00:15:16,233 --> 00:15:16,666
Hua.

346
00:15:17,266 --> 00:15:18,333
Feng Fuliu appeared
at the Northern Bureau.

347
00:15:18,766 --> 00:15:19,433
Commissioner Lu

348
00:15:20,166 --> 00:15:20,400
wants

349
00:15:21,033 --> 00:15:22,266
all Jinyiwei to prepare for battle.

350
00:15:23,700 --> 00:15:24,600
What happened, Duoyu?

351
00:15:24,933 --> 00:15:26,466
What happened, Duoyu?

352
00:15:26,700 --> 00:15:27,300
Feng Fuliu

353
00:15:27,600 --> 00:15:28,833
sent a challenge
to the Northern Bureau.

354
00:15:29,333 --> 00:15:29,866
He says tomorrow night,

355
00:15:30,200 --> 00:15:31,100
he will steal

356
00:15:31,100 --> 00:15:32,366
the Commander's imperial Twin Dragon
Jade.

357
00:15:33,000 --> 00:15:35,200
The whole Northern Bureau is in chaos.

358
00:15:36,000 --> 00:15:37,333
All Northern Bureau officers,
hear my order.

359
00:15:37,533 --> 00:15:38,366
Feng Fuliu

360
00:15:38,666 --> 00:15:41,000
has dared to openly challenge
the Jinyiwei of the Northern Bureau.

361
00:15:41,266 --> 00:15:41,966
As Commissioner,

362
00:15:42,333 --> 00:15:43,066
I order full alert.

363
00:15:43,566 --> 00:15:44,666
Until Feng Fuliu is captured,

364
00:15:45,333 --> 00:15:46,000
no one stands down.

365
00:15:46,500 --> 00:15:48,566
Catch the thief! Catch the thief!

366
00:15:49,000 --> 00:15:49,533
Zuo Da.

367
00:15:49,866 --> 00:15:50,400
Yes.

368
00:15:50,433 --> 00:15:52,000
Take men and set defenses on all sides.

369
00:15:52,233 --> 00:15:52,666
Yes.

370
00:15:52,933 --> 00:15:53,433
Jiang Biao.

371
00:15:53,566 --> 00:15:53,933
Yes.

372
00:15:54,000 --> 00:15:56,433
Take the Commander's written order
to the Ministry of Justice.

373
00:15:56,566 --> 00:15:58,100
Borrow fifty skilled men
from the Enforcement Division

374
00:15:58,200 --> 00:15:59,033
to help guard the bureau.

375
00:15:59,533 --> 00:16:00,033
Yes.

376
00:16:01,566 --> 00:16:03,233
Feng Fuliu.

377
00:16:04,033 --> 00:16:04,800
You dare

378
00:16:05,400 --> 00:16:07,633
openly challenge my Northern Bureau.

379
00:16:10,000 --> 00:16:12,700
I will end your undefeated legend
myself.

380
00:16:12,833 --> 00:16:14,700
Everyone, stay alert.

381
00:16:14,900 --> 00:16:16,566
Search every corner.

382
00:16:16,700 --> 00:16:17,633
Follow the plan.

383
00:16:17,766 --> 00:16:18,366
Yes.

384
00:16:25,866 --> 00:16:26,200
What...

385
00:16:27,000 --> 00:16:28,000
What are you three doing?

386
00:16:28,366 --> 00:16:29,733
You spend all day slacking off,

387
00:16:29,733 --> 00:16:31,066
like your souls have left your bodies.

388
00:16:32,500 --> 00:16:33,600
So you do know

389
00:16:33,900 --> 00:16:35,500
where our souls are.

390
00:16:36,166 --> 00:16:36,433
You...

391
00:16:38,333 --> 00:16:39,533
You two.

392
00:16:39,866 --> 00:16:41,433
Take some men and patrol
the side courtyards.

393
00:16:42,433 --> 00:16:42,933
Shen Bingfan.

394
00:16:43,533 --> 00:16:44,466
You guard the front gate.

395
00:16:44,500 --> 00:16:45,733
Feng Fuliu is skilled in disguise.

396
00:16:46,033 --> 00:16:47,266
You must inspect

397
00:16:47,366 --> 00:16:48,433
everyone entering and leaving.

398
00:16:49,200 --> 00:16:49,633
My lord.

399
00:16:50,033 --> 00:16:51,466
Feng Fuliu is skilled in disguise.

400
00:16:51,933 --> 00:16:53,433
How exactly do we inspect people?

401
00:16:53,533 --> 00:16:53,800
Well...

402
00:16:53,833 --> 00:16:55,000
Do I have to spell it out?

403
00:16:55,000 --> 00:16:56,366
Pinch their faces.

404
00:16:57,333 --> 00:16:58,100
What if

405
00:16:58,533 --> 00:17:01,466
the Commander or you needs
to pass through?

406
00:17:03,066 --> 00:17:04,166
Pinch...

407
00:17:04,200 --> 00:17:05,266
Pinch everyone.

408
00:17:05,500 --> 00:17:06,933
Pinch them hard.

409
00:17:09,533 --> 00:17:10,266
Go, go.

410
00:17:10,333 --> 00:17:10,833
Go.

411
00:17:17,700 --> 00:17:18,533
- Hua!
- Hua!

412
00:17:18,600 --> 00:17:19,633
Hua, pinch me.

413
00:17:21,700 --> 00:17:22,400
Thank you, Hua.

414
00:17:23,200 --> 00:17:25,366
- Move.
- Pinch me. Hua.

415
00:17:26,933 --> 00:17:27,666
Thank you, Hua.

416
00:17:29,200 --> 00:17:30,033
Thank you, Hua.

417
00:17:30,233 --> 00:17:31,800
No rush. No rush.

418
00:17:32,233 --> 00:17:33,233
My turn. My turn.

419
00:17:34,066 --> 00:17:34,633
Mr. Lu.

420
00:17:36,433 --> 00:17:37,300
What is going on here?

421
00:17:37,333 --> 00:17:39,000
Didn't you say

422
00:17:39,100 --> 00:17:41,266
we had to screen everyone?

423
00:17:41,700 --> 00:17:45,733
I'm carrying out the mission.
Face-pinching.

424
00:17:46,233 --> 00:17:46,833
Shen Bingfan.

425
00:17:47,366 --> 00:17:48,933
I told you to check suspicious people.

426
00:17:49,366 --> 00:17:50,733
Why did you call her over?

427
00:17:52,000 --> 00:17:52,933
My hands are too heavy.

428
00:17:53,233 --> 00:17:55,500
I pinched a few men
and sent them all to the clinic.

429
00:17:56,000 --> 00:17:57,866
So I asked Hua to help.

430
00:17:59,433 --> 00:18:01,033
Can you not be gentler?

431
00:18:01,666 --> 00:18:02,833
But you told me

432
00:18:03,200 --> 00:18:04,366
to pinch them hard.

433
00:18:06,866 --> 00:18:08,533
Nonsense. Replace her!

434
00:18:08,733 --> 00:18:10,600
- No!
- Don't replace her!

435
00:18:10,600 --> 00:18:11,500
How dare you?

436
00:18:12,033 --> 00:18:13,533
Why all the noise so early?

437
00:18:14,766 --> 00:18:15,533
Mr. Zhang.

438
00:18:17,366 --> 00:18:19,100
Greetings, Commander.

439
00:18:19,533 --> 00:18:20,366
- What happened?
- I don't know.

440
00:18:20,666 --> 00:18:22,033
How would I know?

441
00:18:40,133 --> 00:18:43,300
♪Because you once entered my dreams♪

442
00:18:43,666 --> 00:18:47,033
♪Truth and illusion blur in wine♪

443
00:18:47,300 --> 00:18:50,300
♪My heart drifted lost♪

444
00:18:50,300 --> 00:18:53,700
♪Yet found you in the crowd♪

445
00:18:54,800 --> 00:18:58,000
♪My blood still burns
as the world surges♪

446
00:18:58,433 --> 00:19:01,766
♪The land is fair, and you are free♪

447
00:19:02,333 --> 00:19:04,533
♪Sword drawn, lost in obsession♪

448
00:19:04,533 --> 00:19:08,566
♪I've softly let it go♪

449
00:19:08,600 --> 00:19:12,466
♪The vow you made was true♪

450
00:19:12,466 --> 00:19:16,200
♪Yet like clouds, it stops for no one♪

451
00:19:16,500 --> 00:19:18,400
♪Put away those dreamlike words♪

452
00:19:18,433 --> 00:19:22,966
♪And forget at world's end♪

453
00:19:23,266 --> 00:19:24,766
♪Embracing memory♪

454
00:19:24,766 --> 00:19:27,133
♪Through blossoms and dreams♪

455
00:19:27,133 --> 00:19:31,000
♪You hide in the crowd, silent♪

456
00:19:31,000 --> 00:19:33,300
♪I wish to let it pass♪

457
00:19:33,333 --> 00:19:38,333
♪And run toward this vast life♪
